Whats new in this version:
* The map has now had displacements added.
* Decals have been added to make the map look not so plain.
* Re-textured the bunkers with a little darker texture
* Revamped bridges (New look, destructible pieces, ropes)
* Input knife area. so feel like a knife fight? what not jump down the gap in the middle :)
* Input lights so it wasn't just a white circle on the walls
*Also input some props

-------------

Final version of this map.
